IMPORTANT INFORMATION - Good Afternoon Families - Our students are very excited for the Wizard's Basketball Game tonight. A few important items to assist you with attending the event.
1. The program is limited strictly to Winchester Public Schools families;
2. Entry to the program will be at the back of the Pearson Building.
2. All students must be accompanied by a parent;
3. Due to capacity issues, entrance will be closed sharply at 6:30 PM. We will begin seating people at 5:30 PM;
4. No strollers or large bags will be permitted;
5. Parking will be challenging;
6. Once you have exited the admissions area, you will not be permitted to re-enter the program;
7. We will have floor seating for students should the bleachers be filled to capacity;
8. Winchester Police Department will be assisting with indoor and exterior monitoring;
9. Food and souvenirs are available for purchase. Food and drink are only permitted in the cafeteria.
10. Should we reach capacity tonight, we will run another program in the Spring.

Most of all, have fun and enjoy the evening!!!

